{
  "sn7.8:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 7.8 ",
  "sn7.8:0.2": "1. Arahantavagga ",
  "sn7.8:0.3": "Aggikasutta ",
  "sn7.8:1.1": "Ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. ",
  "sn7.8:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena aggikabhāradvājassa brāhmaṇassa sappinā pāyaso sannihito hoti: ",
  "sn7.8:1.3": "“aggiṁ juhissāmi, aggihuttaṁ paricarissāmī”ti. ",
  "sn7.8:2.1": "Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṁ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya rājagahaṁ piṇḍāya pāvisi. ",
  "sn7.8:2.2": "Rājagahe sapadānaṁ piṇḍāya caramāno yena aggikabhāradvājassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṁ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṁ aṭṭhāsi. ",
  "sn7.8:2.3": "Addasā kho aggikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ piṇḍāya ṭhitaṁ. ",
  "sn7.8:2.4": "Disvāna bhagavantaṁ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "sn7.8:3.1": "“Tīhi vijjāhi sampanno, ",
  "sn7.8:3.2": "jātimā sutavā bahū; ",
  "sn7.8:3.3": "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, ",
  "sn7.8:3.4": "somaṁ bhuñjeyya pāyasan”ti. ",
  "sn7.8:4.1": "“Bahumpi palapaṁ jappaṁ, ",
  "sn7.8:4.2": "na jaccā hoti brāhmaṇo; ",
  "sn7.8:4.3": "Antokasambu saṅkiliṭṭho, ",
  "sn7.8:4.4": "kuhanāparivārito. ",
  "sn7.8:5.1": "Pubbenivāsaṁ yo vedī, ",
  "sn7.8:5.2": "saggāpāyañca passati; ",
  "sn7.8:5.3": "Atho jātikkhayaṁ patto, ",
  "sn7.8:5.4": "abhiññāvosito muni. ",
  "sn7.8:6.1": "Etāhi tīhi vijjāhi, ",
  "sn7.8:6.2": "tevijjo hoti brāhmaṇo; ",
  "sn7.8:6.3": "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, ",
  "sn7.8:6.4": "somaṁ bhuñjeyya pāyasan”ti. ",
  "sn7.8:7.1": "“Bhuñjatu bhavaṁ gotamo. ",
  "sn7.8:7.2": "Brāhmaṇo bhavan”ti. ",
  "sn7.8:8.1": "“Gāthābhigītaṁ me abhojaneyyaṁ, ",
  "sn7.8:8.2": "Sampassataṁ brāhmaṇa nesa dhammo; ",
  "sn7.8:8.3": "Gāthābhigītaṁ panudanti buddhā, ",
  "sn7.8:8.4": "Dhamme sati brāhmaṇa vuttiresā. ",
  "sn7.8:9.1": "Aññena ca kevalinaṁ mahesiṁ, ",
  "sn7.8:9.2": "Khīṇāsavaṁ kukkuccavūpasantaṁ; ",
  "sn7.8:9.3": "Annena pānena upaṭṭhahassu, ",
  "sn7.8:9.4": "Khettañhi taṁ puññapekkhassa hotī”ti. ",
  "sn7.8:10.1": "Evaṁ vutte, aggikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "sn7.8:10.2": "“abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama …pe… ",
  "sn7.8:10.3": "aññataro ca panāyasmā aggikabhāradvājo arahataṁ ahosīti. "
}